      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Despite being called Forlorn, those elves who live among other species are often quite sociable. These elves gain a +2 racial bonus to @Compendium[sfrpg.skills.QGSqQDA9P7oYQp8z]{Diplomacy} checks and can cast @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.zxecXzHipD4MEoFc]{Comprehend Languages} once per day. At 10th level, they can also cast @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.uWKhr01bnKxuNRkL]{Tongues} once per day.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces elven magic.</strong></p>"
